      <title>特朗普将在陪审团面前出庭作证测试行为举止</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/trump-to-testify-in-carroll-defamation-case-in-test-of-demeanor-in-front-of-jury</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在新罕布什尔州初选取得决定性胜利两天后，唐纳德·特朗普将在纽约出庭作证，反驳作家 E·让·卡罗尔的诽谤指控——测试他影响联邦陪审团和已经与他发生冲突的法官的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/trump-to-testify-in-carroll-defamation-case-in-test-of-demeanor-in-front-of-jury</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利放弃对欧盟为乌克兰提供新武器基金的反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/hungary-reverses-opposition-on-new-eu-weapons-fund-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利将放弃对设立 50 亿欧元（54 亿美元）乌克兰军事援助基金的反对意见，为在成员国解决技术问题后达成协议，改进旨在稳定向基辅供应武器的工具铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/hungary-reverses-opposition-on-new-eu-weapons-fund-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:28:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国议员遭持石袭击者袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/south-korea-ruling-party-lawmaker-attacked-in-seoul-yonhap-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国执政党表示，一名韩国执政党议员在首尔街头被一名挥舞石块的袭击者击中头部，随后被送往医院，伤势似乎没有生命危险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/south-korea-ruling-party-lawmaker-attacked-in-seoul-yonhap-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:19:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>议长称匈牙利议会不会催促瑞典加入北约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/hungarian-parliament-won-t-rush-sweden-s-nato-bid-speaker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利议会议长表示，在土耳其批准瑞典加入北约后，布达佩斯政府本周成为最后一个拒绝批准瑞典加入北约的国家，议会并不急于批准瑞典加入北约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/hungarian-parliament-won-t-rush-sweden-s-nato-bid-speaker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:16:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国极右翼仍有望赢得地区选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/uproar-against-german-far-right-hasn-t-dented-support-in-saxony</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国另类选择党仍有望赢得9月份萨克森州的选举，这表明最近针对极右翼政党的抗议活动并没有削弱其在德累斯顿周边东部地区的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/uproar-against-german-far-right-hasn-t-dented-support-in-saxony</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:08:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>抗议活动不断蔓延，欧盟试图安抚农民的愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/eu-tries-to-soothe-farmers-anger-as-protests-keep-spreading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌尔苏拉·冯德莱恩周四表示，现在是解决农业问题上日益扩大的分歧的时候了，她试图回应农民对欧洲关键选举年绿色政策和补贴削减的日益强烈的抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/eu-tries-to-soothe-farmers-anger-as-protests-keep-spreading</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 08:46:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯南部图阿普谢炼油厂一夜之间发生火灾受损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/russia-s-southern-tuapse-oil-refinery-damaged-in-a-fire-overnight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四早些时候，俄罗斯石油公司位于俄罗斯黑海沿岸的图阿普谢主要炼油厂发生火灾，这是乌克兰无人机袭击导致该国下游和能源出口设施发生一系列事件中的最新一起。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/russia-s-southern-tuapse-oil-refinery-damaged-in-a-fire-overnight</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 07:50:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国前总理领跑者在第一个法庭案件结案后重返议会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/former-thai-prime-minister-frontrunner-returns-to-parliament-after-court-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国最高法院清除了泰国反对党议员皮塔·林贾罗恩拉 (Pita Limjaroenrat) 违反选举规则的指控一天后，他重返议会，并发誓要审查包括数十亿泰铢现金发放计划在内的政府政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/former-thai-prime-minister-frontrunner-returns-to-parliament-after-court-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 06:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国公众批评官员因火灾造成39人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/chinese-public-lashes-out-at-officials-over-fire-that-killed-39</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国民众因一场导致 39 人死亡（其中包括学生）的火灾而猛烈抨击官员——在今年年初发生一系列致命事故后，这一事件促使习近平主席呼吁加大力度确保公共安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/chinese-public-lashes-out-at-officials-over-fire-that-killed-39</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 04:11:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国官员要求习近平继续实行勒紧裤腰带的政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/china-economy-local-officials-cut-costs-after-xi-s-call-for-belt-tightening</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府会议上不提供文具，禁止出现华丽的建筑，并禁止检查员在官方活动中监视浪费的食物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/china-economy-local-officials-cut-costs-after-xi-s-call-for-belt-tightening</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
